      "content": "rebuild? how? there is no rebuilding from this. i am thousands of people's responsibility and i failed them all. it's not just some bad day, it's a permanent disaster. i feel like i'm just trapped in this nightmare and there's no version of the future where i'm not just a walking embarrassment. it feels like the only way to make the feeling stop is to just... not be here anymore.",
